review_blob: 750ml bottle two months old - very young, fresh and fantastic! great nose, drank well.
I have had Cynthiana on tap and 750ml bottle - I liked the bottle slightly better - probably one of my favorite Saint Somewhere beers. crisp and semi dry - love it!
You can taste the Palmetto berries and whole Hibiscus flowers...  My favorite of Saint Somewhere Brewing Company. well done.
